3) Получние параметров продукции
GET /eshop/api/v1/?type=get-features&token={token}

Пример ответа:
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "name": "test",
      "position": "0",
      "ftype": "0",
      "fdefault": "123",
      "foptions": "",
      "in_filter": "0",
      "required": "0"
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "name": "test2",
      "position": "0",
      "ftype": "2",
      "fdefault": "2",
      "foptions": "{\"1\":\"t1\",\"2\":\"t2\"}",
      "in_filter": "1",
      "required": "0"
    }
  ],
  "status": "OK"
}

4) Получение вариантов продукции
GET /eshop/api/v1/?type=get-variants&token={token}[&product_id={ID}]

Пример ответа:
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "9",
      "product_id": "2",
      "sku": "",
      "name": "\u0421\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0439",
      "price": "12.00",
      "compare_price": "24.00",
      "stock": "5",
      "position": "0",
      "amount": "88",
      "attachment": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "8",
      "product_id": "2",
      "sku": "",
      "name": "\u041a\u0440\u0430\u0441\u043d\u044b\u0439",
      "price": "11.00",
      "compare_price": "22.00",
      "stock": "5",
      "position": "0",
      "amount": "3",
      "attachment": ""
    }
  ],
  "status": "OK"
}

5) Обновление статуса заказа
POST /eshop/api/v1/?type=update-order-statuses&token={token}

Пример запроса:
[
  {
    "order_id" : "1",
    "status": "1"
  },
  {
    "order_id" : "2",
    "status": "0"
  }
]

Пример ответа:
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "status": "OK"
    },
    {
      "id": "",
      "status": "error",
      "message": "Item with this ID does not exist"
    }
  ],
  "status": "OK"
}

